import React from 'react'; import { Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Button } from '@mui/material'; const InstructorTable = ({ currentItems, handleClickOpen }) => { return ( Id VenueId FirstName LastName State City PhoneNumber Email Wage Per Hour Total Classes Times Deposit Rent Manikin Numbers Finance Rent Status Fob Key {Array.isArray(currentItems) && currentItems.length > 0 ? ( currentItems.map((instructor) => ( {instructor.id} {instructor.venueId} {instructor.firstname} {instructor.lastname} {instructor.state} {instructor.city} {instructor.phoneNumber} {instructor.email} {instructor.wageHour} {instructor.totalClassTimes} {instructor.deposit} {instructor.rentManikinNumbers} {instructor.finance} {instructor.rentStatus} {instructor.fobKey} )) ) : ( No data available )}
); }; export default InstructorTable;
